The funeral of Sarah Malema, EFF leader Julius Malema's grandmother is being held in Seshego. Courtesy of #DSTV403 SESHEGO - The funeral of the late Sarah Malema, the grandmother of EFF leader, Julius Malema took place in Polokwane on Saturday. Koko Sarah, as she's affectionately known, passed away last Saturday in her home in Seshego. Her death came just weeks after Malema buried another relative. READ: Malema's grandmother dies EFF leaders have gathered in Seshego for the funeral. Messages of condolences are still pouring in from South Africans across the country. Amongst those in attendance are Rivonia triallist, Andrew Mlangeni, businessman, Patrice Motsepe and representatives from the Mandela family.